---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import '../styles/global.css';
import Gallery from '../components/Gallery.astro';
import heroImageWebp from '../assets/On_The_Moon_ZW_111kopie.webp';
import ethLogo from '../assets/eth_logo_kurz_neg.webp';
import uniBernLogo from '../assets/uni bern logo.webp';
import swissSpaceMuseumLogo from '../assets/swiss space museum logo.webp';
import zirkusQuartierLogo from '../assets/zirkus quartier logo.webp';
import kukoLogo from '../assets/KuKo Logo.webp';
---

<html lang="de" class="scroll-smooth">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<link rel="preload" href="/fonts/manrope-latin-wght-normal.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin />
		<meta name="description" content="ON THE MOON - Eine Kreation der Cie. Youkali. Luftakrobatik, Physical Theatre und Live-Sound." />
		<title>ON THE MOON | Cie. Youkali</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-zinc-950 font-sans leading-relaxed text-zinc-100 antialiased">
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="relative flex min-h-screen items-start overflow-hidden">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 after:absolute after:inset-0 after:bg-gradient-to-b after:from-black/30 after:via-black/10 after:to-black/60 after:content-['']">
				<Image
					src={heroImageWebp}
					alt="ON THE MOON Performance"
					widths={[640, 1024, 1920]}
					sizes="100vw"
					quality={80}
					loading="eager"
					class="h-full w-full object-cover object-center"
				/>
			</div>
			<div class="relative z-10 mt-8 px-6 py-12 md:px-10">
				<p class="-mt-6 mb-10 pl-1 text-[2rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] opacity-90">Cie. Youkali</p>
				<h1 class="mb-4 text-[clamp(6rem,26vw,9rem)] font-bold leading-none tracking-[0.03em] [text-shadow:2px_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">ON THE MOON</h1>
			</div>
			<p class="absolute bottom-2.5 right-2.5 z-20 m-0 max-w-[calc(100%-4rem)] text-xs opacity-60 md:max-w-none">© David Schelker</p>
			<a href="#about" class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 z-10 -translate-x-1/2 text-white/70 transition hover:text-white hover:no-underline" aria-label="Scroll down">
				<svg class="animate-bounce" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
					<path d="M7 13l5 5 5-5M7 6l5 5 5-5"/>
				</svg>
			</a>
		</section>

		<!-- About Section -->
		<section id="about" class="bg-zinc-950 py-16 md:py-24">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[900px] px-6 md:px-8">
				<p class="mb-8 text-[1.15rem] font-normal leading-[1.8] sm:text-[1.35rem]">
					Umwoben von Geschichten, gehört er bisher nur den Träumenden und sich selbst. Doch was, wenn wieder Menschen auf dem Mond landen? Wenn der Mond erobert und dauerhaft bewohnt wird?
				</p>
				<p class="mb-6">
					ON THE MOON beschäftigt sich mit Besitz, anhand des Umgangs von Menschen mit dem Mond. Drei Performer:innen und ein Musiker begeben sich auf eine bilderreiche Reise ins All und erforschen zwischen Fakten und Fantasie ungewöhnliche Zukunftsutopien. Mit Luftakrobatik, Physical Theatre und Live-Sound geht das Projekt innovative Wege im zeitgenössischen Zirkus: Es verbindet Wissenschaft mit Zirkus in weitgehendem Sinne und lädt das Publikum zu einer spielerischen Reise ein.
				</p>
				<p class="mb-6">
					Im Frühjahr 2025 wurde das Projekt von Migros Kulturprozent für eine Ideationsphase unterstützt. Ab Juni 2026 startet die Stückkreation, in Koproduktion mit dem Zirkusquartier Zürich, begleitet von Wissenschaftler:innen der ETH Zürich und der Uni Bern.
				</p>
				<div class="mt-12 flex flex-col gap-4 pt-8 uppercase opacity-80 md:flex-row md:flex-wrap md:gap-6">
					<span class="inline-flex items-center before:mr-3 before:inline-block before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-[#9b59b6] before:content-['']">Ab 7 Jahren</span>
					<span class="inline-flex items-center before:mr-3 before:inline-block before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-[#9b59b6] before:content-['']">Dauer: ca. 60 Minuten</span>
					<span class="inline-flex items-center before:mr-3 before:inline-block before:size-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-[#9b59b6] before:content-['']">Spielbar in Theatern und Turnhallen</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Gallery Section -->
		<section class="bg-zinc-950 py-10 md:py-14">
			<Gallery />
		</section>

		<!-- Team Section -->
		<section id="team" class="bg-[#111] py-16 md:py-[4.5rem]">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[900px] px-6 md:px-8">
				<h2 class="mb-8 text-[clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4rem)] font-extrabold leading-tight">Mitwirkende</h2>
				<div class="grid gap-6 md:gap-7">

						<div class="grid gap-3">
							<div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-1">
								<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">Künstlerische Leitung, Produktionsleitung</span>
								<span class="leading-[1.42]"><a class="border-b border-white/30 text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-white hover:text-white hover:no-underline" href="https://www.valeavolcker.com/aktuelles" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Valea Völcker</a></span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-1">
								<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">Idee & Performance</span>
								<span class="leading-[1.42]">
									Valea Völcker,
									<a class="border-b border-white/30 text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-white hover:text-white hover:no-underline" href="https://simonthoeni.ch/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Simon Thöni</a>,
									<a class="border-b border-white/30 text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-white hover:text-white hover:no-underline" href="https://www.dianegemsch.ch/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Diane Gemsch</a>
								</span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-1">
								<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">Sound & Performance</span>
								<span class="leading-[1.42]"><a class="border-b border-white/30 text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-white hover:text-white hover:no-underline" href="https://www.marquismcgee.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marquis' McGee</a></span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-1">
								<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">End-Regie</span>
								<span class="leading-[1.42]">Newa Grawit (<a class="border-b border-white/30 text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-white hover:text-white hover:no-underline" href="https://cirquedeloin.ch/companie/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cirque de Loin</a>)</span>
							</div>



							<div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-1">
								<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">Wissenschaftliche Begleitung</span>
								<span class="leading-[1.42]">Prof. Audrey Vorburger (Uni Bern), Dr. Anna Mittelholz (ETH Zürich), Prof. Dr. Henner Busemann (ETH Zürich)</span>
							</div>
				

							<div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-1">
								<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">Bühnenbild</span>
								<span class="leading-[1.42]"><a class="border-b border-white/30 text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-white hover:text-white hover:no-underline" href="https://annatinahuwiler.ch/z-BERG" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Annatina Huwiler</a></span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-1">
								<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">Produktions-Mentoring</span>
								<span class="leading-[1.42]"><a class="border-b border-white/30 text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-white hover:text-white hover:no-underline" href="https://bollwerk-andreaboll.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Andrea Boll</a></span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-1">
								<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">Luftakrobatik Coaching</span>
								<span class="leading-[1.42]"><a class="border-b border-white/30 text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-white hover:text-white hover:no-underline" href="https://www.rebekkagather.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rebekka Gather</a></span>
							</div>
							<div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-1">
								<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">Rigging Beratung</span>
								<span class="leading-[1.42]">Duncan Cown</span>
							</div>




							
						</div>
					</div>

			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Dates Section -->
		<section id="dates" class="bg-zinc-950 py-16 md:py-24">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[900px] px-6 md:px-8">
				<h2 class="mb-8 text-[clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4rem)] font-extrabold leading-tight">Daten 2026</h2>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
					<a href="https://zeughaus-areal.ch/kulturmaerz-2026/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col gap-1 border-l-[3px] border-transparent bg-white/[0.03] p-6 no-underline transition hover:border-[#9b59b6] hover:bg-[#9b59b6]/10">
						<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">16.-19. März</span>
						<span class=" text-[1.15rem] font-normal sm:text-[1.35rem]">Workshops mit Schulklassen, Kulturmärz Uster</span>
					</a>
					<a href="https://swissspacemuseum.ch/events/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col gap-1 border-l-[3px] border-transparent bg-white/[0.03] p-6 no-underline transition hover:border-[#9b59b6] hover:bg-[#9b59b6]/10">
						<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">27. September</span>
						<span class="text-[1.15rem] font-normal sm:text-[1.35rem]">Podiumsdiskussion, Swiss Space Museum Regensdorf</span>
					</a>
					<a href="https://zirkusquartier.ch/programm/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col gap-1 border-l-[3px] border-transparent bg-white/[0.03] p-6 no-underline transition hover:border-[#9b59b6] hover:bg-[#9b59b6]/10">
						<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">23. Oktober</span>
						<span class="text-[1.15rem] font-normal sm:text-[1.35rem]">PREMIERE, Zirkusquartier Zürich</span>
					</a>
					<a href="https://zirkusquartier.ch/programm/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col gap-1 border-l-[3px] border-transparent bg-white/[0.03] p-6 no-underline transition hover:border-[#9b59b6] hover:bg-[#9b59b6]/10">
						<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">24./25. Oktober</span>
						<span class="text-[1.15rem] font-normal sm:text-[1.35rem]">Zirkusquartier Zürich</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Video Section -->
		<section id="video" class="bg-[#111] py-16 md:py-24">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[900px] px-6 md:px-8">
				<h2 class="mb-8 text-[clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4rem)] font-extrabold leading-tight">Teaser</h2>
				<div class="relative aspect-video overflow-hidden rounded">
					<iframe 
						src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/4iZVH2jsz0E?rel=0" 
						title="ON THE MOON – Ideationsphase"
						frameborder="0" 
						allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
						referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
						allowfullscreen
						loading="lazy"
						class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full"
					></iframe>
				</div>
				<p class="mb-0 mt-4 text-sm opacity-60">© Michael Gärtner, Wetzikon TV</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Contact Section -->
		<section id="contact" class="bg-zinc-950 py-16 md:py-24">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[900px] px-6 md:px-8">
				<h2 class="mb-8 text-[clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4rem)] font-extrabold leading-tight">Kontakt</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12">
					<div>
						<h3 class="mb-4 text-base uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">Produktionsleitung</h3>
						<p class="mb-2">Valea Völcker</p>
						<p class="mb-2"><a class="border-b border-white/30 text-zinc-200 transition hover:border-white hover:text-white hover:no-underline" href="mailto:info@valeavolcker.com">info@valeavolcker.com</a></p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="mb-4 text-base uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">Verein Youkali – Cie. Youkali</h3>
						<p class="mb-2">Morgenstrasse 30</p>
						<p class="mb-2">8620 Wetzikon</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Partners Section -->
		<footer class="bg-[#111] py-16 text-center">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[900px] px-6 md:px-8">
				<div class="mb-12">
					<p class="mb-8 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">In Zusammenarbeit mit</p>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-10">
						<a href="https://ethz.ch/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><Image src={ethLogo} alt="ETH Zürich" class="h-20 w-auto opacity-80 transition duration-300 hover:scale-[1.08] hover:opacity-100" /></a>
						<a href="https://www.unibe.ch/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><Image src={uniBernLogo} alt="Universität Bern" class="h-20 w-auto opacity-80 transition duration-300 hover:scale-[1.08] hover:opacity-100" /></a>
						<a href="https://swissspacemuseum.ch/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><Image src={swissSpaceMuseumLogo} alt="Swiss Space Museum" class="h-20 w-auto opacity-80 transition duration-300 hover:scale-[1.08] hover:opacity-100 [filter:invert(1)_grayscale(1)] [mix-blend-mode:screen]" /></a>
						<a href="https://zirkusquartier.ch/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><Image src={zirkusQuartierLogo} alt="Zirkusquartier Zürich" class="h-20 w-auto opacity-80 transition duration-300 hover:scale-[1.08] hover:opacity-100 [filter:invert(1)_grayscale(1)] [mix-blend-mode:screen]" /></a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="mb-8 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.015em] opacity-40">Unterstützt von</p>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-10">
						<Image src={kukoLogo} alt="Kultur Kommission Wetzikon" class="h-20 w-auto opacity-80 transition duration-300 hover:scale-[1.08] hover:opacity-100 [filter:invert(1)_grayscale(1)] [mix-blend-mode:screen]" />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
